Also, don‚Äôt miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With ‚ÄúAvatar: Fire and Ash,‚Äù James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na‚Äôvi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na‚Äôvi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Salda√±a), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

Goddess Katyayani, the sixth form of Maa Durga, is worshipped on the sixth day of Navratri. She is the powerful warrior goddess who destroys evil forces and grants strength, courage, and victory. snippet.title: Vazhiyiraen - Full Video | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini Vasanth | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil unveils the full video "Vazhiyiraen", the latest single from the highly anticipated film Madharaasi, written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth, Vazhiyiraen stands out as an emotionally rich and visually stunning track that beautifully captures themes of love, hope, and longing. With Anirudh Ravichander‚Äôs heartfelt composition and soul-touching vocals, the song resonates deeply, offering a cinematic musical experience that lingers long after it ends.

Set against picturesque visuals and brought to life by the tender chemistry between the lead pair, Vazhiyiraen is quickly becoming a fan favorite among Tamil romantic songs 2025. Perfect for those who enjoy melodious love songs, Anirudh hits, and lyrical storytelling, this track adds emotional depth to the Madharaasi soundtrack. Don't miss this musical gem that's already trending under #VazhiyiraenSong, a must-watch for fans of Sivakarthikeyan movies, AR Murugadoss direction, and Tamil film music at its finest.

en.description:
Junglee Music Tamil unveils the full video "Vazhiyiraen", the latest single from the highly anticipated film Madharaasi, written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth, Vazhiyiraen stands out as an emotionally rich and visually stunning track that beautifully captures themes of love, hope, and longing. With Anirudh Ravichander‚Äôs heartfelt composition and soul-touching vocals, the song resonates deeply, offering a cinematic musical experience that lingers long after it ends.

Set against picturesque visuals and brought to life by the tender chemistry between the lead pair, Vazhiyiraen is quickly becoming a fan favorite among Tamil romantic songs 2025. Perfect for those who enjoy melodious love songs, Anirudh hits, and lyrical storytelling, this track adds emotional depth to the Madharaasi soundtrack. Don't miss this musical gem that's already trending under #VazhiyiraenSong, a must-watch for fans of Sivakarthikeyan movies, AR Murugadoss direction, and Tamil film music at its finest.
